domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Batch Fields
domains.description: The user is prompted for batch properties once for each set of runs they import. The batch is a convenience to let users set properties that seldom change in one place and import many runs using them. This is the first step of the import process.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Run Fields
domains.description: The user is prompted to enter run level properties for each file they import.  This is the second step of the import process.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Sample Fields
domains.description: The user will be prompted to enter these properties for each of the sample well groups in their chosen plate template.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Antigen Fields
domains.description: The user will be prompted to enter these properties for each of the antigen well groups in their chosen plate template.

domains.name: ELISpot Assay Test Analyte Fields
domains.description: The user will be prompted to enter these properties for each of the analyte well groups
